&lt;h1 id="happiness-is-a-skill-you-can-develop"&gt;Happiness Is a Skill You Can Develop&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Feb 3 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&amp;rsquo;re not stuck at your current level of happiness&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The first step to increasing your level of happiness is realizing you can. This is where a lot of people get tripped up. For the vast majority of people, some of their happiness—probably a lot more than they think—is in their control.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>The Need for Indifference</title><link>https://linguista.cn/naval/orig/the-need-for-indifference/</link><pubDate>Fri, 04 Jan 2019 05:41:56 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/naval/orig/the-need-for-indifference/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/naval/zh/the-need-for-indifference.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
